S|# 17 · Newsletter (Posts)|> A full nl studio integrated with the **Kit** API — compose, design, broadcast, run sequences/automations, and analyze cg. The owner is starting a monthly nl as part of the Life OS.
S|Purpose|Bring email newsletters into Mission Control. Integrated with **Kit** (formerly ConvertKit) via its API, it helps **analyze subscribers, compose/write/design** the nl, **manage and analyze cg**, and potentially write **automations/sequences**. The stated near-term goal is a **monthly nl**.
S|Page header|- Title: **nl**, breadcrumb `Vibe with AI / nl`. // - Sub-line: "Mission Control → KIT · broadcasts · lifecycle sequences, measured on clicks, replies & conversions." // - **Connected to KIT** status, **Visit workspace**, **API healthy**, last-sync time. // - Buttons: **Open in Kit** and **New broadcast**. // - A note: "Matching powers Vahalla behind the same interface."
S|Tabs|A horizontal tab bar drives the page: **Audience**, **Compose**, **Broadcasts**, **Sequences**, **Growth**, **anl**. // ### Audience // - **Subscriber metrics** — total subscribers (e.g. **128**) with a trend sparkline, **new subscribers** (+12), unsubscribes (2), etc. // - **By tag / segment** breakdown — counts per audience segment: e.g. **nl 128**, **Course waitlist 41**, **In subscribers / app users 63**, **Consulting leads**, **Dormant (90d) 11**, etc. — so the owner can target broadcasts t
S|Right rail (live preview)|- A **live email preview** of the current issue branded to the workspace ("Vibe with AI"), e.g. *"I stopped building dashboards…"* with a **Try in [Kit]** CTA — a WYSIWYG of what subscribers receive.
S|Agents & integration|- **William** drafts/composes; the agt designs sequences and proposes copy. // - All sending flows through the **Kit API**; the send action is human-gated until trust is built (consistent with the email/soc draft-first pattern).